{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852171885,"sessionID":"ses_286f6aed7ffekYy405f9z7HzpW","part":{"id":"prt_d7909a736001wtT2jfOnb4dMCB","messageID":"msg_d79098e1f001RKzOFBTlW23LEV","sessionID":"ses_286f6aed7ffekYy405f9z7HzpW","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-b5799627feb741b9b26dd5df8b37d648","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 Proposal\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: 为 Router 模块提供标准化的 JWT 认证与签发能力，支持服务间安全通信和用户身份验证。\n5: \n6: ## Scope\n7: ### In Scope\n8: | Deliverable | Description |\n9: |-------------|-------------|\n10: | JWT 签发 | 生成标准 JWT Token |\n11: | Token 验证 | 中间件验证 Token 有效性 |\n12: | Token 刷新 | 支持长效 Token 的刷新机制 |\n13: \n14: ### Out of Scope\n15: - OAuth2 协议实现\n16: - 第三方身份提供商集成\n17: - 细粒度权限控制\n18: \n19: ## Impact Analysis\n20: ### Upstream Dependencies\n21: | Dependency | Impact |\n22: |------------|--------|\n23: | pkg/config | 配置读取（密钥、过期时间） |\n24: | pkg/logger | 日志记录 |\n25: \n26: ### Downstream Consumers\n27: | Consumer | Usage |\n28: |----------|-------|\n29: | HTTP Handlers | 认证中间件保护 |\n30: | gRPC Services | Token 验证 |\n31: \n32: ## Alternatives Considered\n33: ### Alternative 1: 使用现成 JWT 库\n34: | Pros | Cons |\n35: |------|------|\n36: | 成熟稳定 | 可能存在冗余功能 |\n37: | 社区支持 | 需要适配现有架构 |\n38: \n39: ### Alternative 2: 自实现 JWT 逻辑\n40: | Pros | Cons |\n41: |------|------|\n42: | 完全可控 | 安全风险高 |\n43: | 轻量 | 维护成本高 |\n44: \n45: **推荐方案**: Alternative 1 - 使用成熟 JWT 库（如 golang-jwt/jwt）\n46: \n47: ## Risks\n48: | Risk | Mitigation |\n49: |------|------------|\n50: | 密钥泄露 | 使用环境变量或密钥管理服务 |\n51: | Token 被劫持 | 支持 Token 黑名单机制 |\n52: | 时钟不同步 | 引入合理的时钟偏差容忍 |\n53: \n54: ## Implementation Notes\n55: 1. 使用 golang-jwt/jwt v5 作为基础库\n56: 2. 支持 HS256 和 RS256 两种签名算法\n57: 3. Token 默认过期时间 24 小时\n58: 4. 刷新 Token 有效期 7 天\n59: \n60: ## References\n61: - [golang-jwt/jwt](https://github.com/golang-jwt/jwt)\n62: - [RFC 7519 - JSON Web Token](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519)\n\n(End of file - total 62 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n为 Router 模块提供标准化的 JWT 认证与签发能力，支持服务间安全通信和用户身份验证。\n\n## Scope\n### In Scope\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| JWT 签发 | 生成标准 JWT Token |\n| Token 验证 | 中间件验证 Token 有效性 |\n| Token 刷新 | 支持长效 Token 的刷新机制 |\n\n### Out of Scope\n- OAuth2 协议实现\n- 第三方身份提供商集成\n- 细粒度权限控制\n\n## Impact Analysis\n### Upstream Dependencies","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775852171863,"end":1775852171884}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852171887,"sessionID":"ses_286f6aed7ffekYy405f9z7HzpW","part":{"id":"prt_d7909aaa0001DnZ6juMzIAihcK","messageID":"msg_d79098e1f001RKzOFBTlW23LEV","sessionID":"ses_286f6aed7ffekYy405f9z7HzpW","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-b5f01886fabe43d7b99def02fea3034a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/jwt.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/jwt.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package router\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"context\"\n5: \t\"crypto/rand\"\n6: \t\"crypto/rsa\"\n7: \t\"crypto/x509\"\n8: \t\"encoding/pem\"\n9: \t\"fmt\"\n10: \t\"os\"\n11: \t\"time\"\n12: \n13: \t\"github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5\"\n14: \t\"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n15: )\n16: \n17: const (\n18: \trsaKeySize         = 2048\n19: \tjwtExpiration      = 5 * time.Minute\n20: \tIdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"\n21: \tPrivateKeyDataKey  = \"private.pem\"\n22: \tPublicKeyDataKey   = \"public.pem\"\n23: )\n24: \n25: var IdentityNamespace = \"default\"\n26: \n27: func init() {\n28: \tif ns := os.Getenv(\"AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE\"); ns != \"\" {\n29: \t\tIdentityNamespace = ns\n30: \t}\n31: }\n32: \n33: type JWTManager struct {\n34: \tprivateKey *rsa.PrivateKey\n35: \tpublicKey  *rsa.PublicKey\n36: }\n37: \n38: func NewJWTManager() (*JWTManager, error) {\n39: \tprivateKey, err := rsa.GenerateKey(rand.Reader, rsaKeySize)\n40: \tif err != nil {\n41: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to generate RSA key: %w\", err)\n42: \t}\n43: \n44: \treturn &JWTManager{\n45: \t\tprivateKey: privateKey,\n46: \t\tpublicKey:  &privateKey.PublicKey,\n47: \t}, nil\n48: }\n49: \n50: func (j *JWTManager) GenerateToken(claims map[string]interface{}) (string, error) {\n51: \tnow := time.Now()\n52: \n53: \ttokenClaims := jwt.MapClaims{\n54: \t\t\"exp\": now.Add(jwtExpiration).Unix(),\n55: \t\t\"iat\": now.Unix(),\n56: \t\t\"iss\": \"agentcube-router\",\n57: \t}\n58: \n59: \tfor k, v := range claims {\n60: \t\ttokenClaims[k] = v\n61: \t}\n62: \n63: \ttoken := jwt.NewWithClaims(jwt.SigningMethodRS256, tokenClaims)\n64: \n65: \ttokenString, err := token.SignedString(j.privateKey)\n66: \tif err != nil {\n67: \t\treturn \"\", &JWTSigningError{Err: err}\n68: \t}\n69: \n70: \treturn tokenString, nil\n71: }\n72: \n73: func (j *JWTManager) TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx context.Context) error {\n74: \tklog.Warningf(\"not in cluster, skipping secret persistence\")\n75: \treturn nil\n76: }\n77: \n78: func encodePrivateKeyPEM(key *rsa.PrivateKey) []byte {\n79: \treturn pem.EncodeToMemory(&pem.Block{\n80: \t\tType:  \"RSA PRIVATE KEY\",\n81: \t\tBytes: x509.MarshalPKCS1PrivateKey(key),\n82: \t})\n83: }\n84: \n85: func encodePublicKeyPEM(key *rsa.PublicKey) []byte {\n86: \tbytes, err := x509.MarshalPKIXPublicKey(key)\n87: \tif err != nil {\n88: \t\treturn nil\n89: \t}\n90: \treturn pem.EncodeToMemory(&pem.Block{\n91: \t\tType:  \"PUBLIC KEY\",\n92: \t\tBytes: bytes,\n93: \t})\n94: }\n95: \n96: func loadPrivateKeyPEM(data []byte) (*rsa.PrivateKey, error) {\n97: \tblock, _ := pem.Decode(data)\n98: \tif block == nil {\n99: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to decode PEM block\")\n100: \t}\n101: \n102: \tkey, err := x509.ParsePKCS1PrivateKey(block.Bytes)\n103: \tif err != nil {\n104: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to parse private key: %w\", err)\n105: \t}\n106: \n107: \treturn key, nil\n108: }\n109: \n110: func (j *JWTManager) GetPublicKey() *rsa.PublicKey {\n111: \treturn j.publicKey\n112: }\n\n(End of file - total 112 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package router\n\nimport (\n\t\"context\"\n\t\"crypto/rand\"\n\t\"crypto/rsa\"\n\t\"crypto/x509\"\n\t\"encoding/pem\"\n\t\"fmt\"\n\t\"os\"\n\t\"time\"\n\n\t\"github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5\"\n\t\"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n)\n\nconst (\n\trsaKeySize         = 2048\n\tjwtExpiration      = 5 * time.Minute\n\tIdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/jwt.go","time":{"start":1775852171866,"end":1775852171886}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852171889,"sessionID":"ses_286f6aed7ffekYy405f9z7HzpW","part":{"id":"prt_d7909ae68001T4ZF9R5HFmRESv","messageID":"msg_d79098e1f001RKzOFBTlW23LEV","sessionID":"ses_286f6aed7ffekYy405f9z7HzpW","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-cbaf0402d99647d0835778cd11ba0c62","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/middleware.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/middleware.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package router\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"net/http\"\n5: \t\"time\"\n6: \n7: \t\"github.com/gin-gonic/gin\"\n8: )\n9: \n10: func concurrencyLimitMiddleware(maxConcurrent int) gin.HandlerFunc {\n11: \tif maxConcurrent <= 0 {\n12: \t\tmaxConcurrent = 1000\n13: \t}\n14: \n15: \tsem := make(chan struct{}, maxConcurrent)\n16: \n17: \treturn func(c *gin.Context) {\n18: \t\tselect {\n19: \t\tcase sem <- struct{}{}:\n20: \t\t\tdefer func() { <-sem }()\n21: \t\t\tc.Next()\n22: \t\tdefault:\n23: \t\t\tc.JSON(http.StatusTooManyRequests, gin.H{\n24: \t\t\t\t\"error\": \"server overloaded, please try again later\",\n25: \t\t\t\t\"code\":  \"SERVER_OVERLOADED\",\n26: \t\t\t})\n27: \t\t\tc.Abort()\n28: \t\t}\n29: \t}\n30: }\n31: \n32: func loggingMiddleware(logger Logger) gin.HandlerFunc {\n33: \treturn func(c *gin.Context) {\n34: \t\tstart := time.Now()\n35: \n36: \t\tc.Next()\n37: \n38: \t\tif logger == nil {\n39: \t\t\treturn\n40: \t\t}\n41: \n42: \t\tduration := time.Since(start)\n43: \t\tstatus := c.Writer.Status()\n44: \n45: \t\tlogger.Info(\"request\",\n46: \t\t\t\"method\", c.Request.Method,\n47: \t\t\t\"path\", c.Request.URL.Path,\n48: \t\t\t\"status\", status,\n49: \t\t\t\"duration\", duration,\n50: \t\t)\n51: \t}\n52: }\n53: \n54: func recoveryMiddleware(logger Logger) gin.HandlerFunc {\n55: \treturn func(c *gin.Context) {\n56: \t\tdefer func() {\n57: \t\t\tif err := recover(); err != nil {\n58: \t\t\t\tif logger != nil {\n59: \t\t\t\t\tlogger.Error(\"panic recovered\",\n60: \t\t\t\t\t\t\"error\", err,\n61: \t\t\t\t\t\t\"path\", c.Request.URL.Path,\n62: \t\t\t\t\t\t\"method\", c.Request.Method,\n63: \t\t\t\t\t)\n64: \t\t\t\t}\n65: \n66: \t\t\t\tc.JSON(http.StatusInternalServerError, gin.H{\n67: \t\t\t\t\t\"error\": \"internal server error\",\n68: \t\t\t\t})\n69: \t\t\t\tc.Abort()\n70: \t\t\t}\n71: \t\t}()\n72: \t\tc.Next()\n73: \t}\n74: }\n\n(End of file - total 74 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package router\n\nimport (\n\t\"net/http\"\n\t\"time\"\n\n\t\"github.com/gin-gonic/gin\"\n)\n\nfunc concurrencyLimitMiddleware(maxConcurrent int) gin.HandlerFunc {\n\tif maxConcurrent <= 0 {\n\t\tmaxConcurrent = 1000\n\t}\n\n\tsem := make(chan struct{}, maxConcurrent)\n\n\treturn func(c *gin.Context) {\n\t\tselect {\n\t\tcase sem <- struct{}{}:\n\t\t\tdefer func() { <-sem }()","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/middleware.go","time":{"start":1775852171868,"end":1775852171888}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852171891,"sessionID":"ses_286f6aed7ffekYy405f9z7HzpW","part":{"id":"prt_d7909b23b0010q2ecyVdWti8hP","messageID":"msg_d79098e1f001RKzOFBTlW23LEV","sessionID":"ses_286f6aed7ffekYy405f9z7HzpW","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-afaa676c4d824a53bcde1ac00f7e4400","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/config.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/config.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package router\n2: \n3: type Config struct {\n4: \tPort                  string\n5: \tEnableTLS             bool\n6: \tTLSCert               string\n7: \tTLSKey                string\n8: \tMaxConcurrentRequests int\n9: \tDebug                 bool\n10: }\n11: \n12: func DefaultConfig() *Config {\n13: \treturn &Config{\n14: \t\tPort:                  \":8080\",\n15: \t\tEnableTLS:             false,\n16: \t\tMaxConcurrentRequests: 1000,\n17: \t\tDebug:                 false,\n18: \t}\n19: }\n\n(End of file - total 19 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package router\n\ntype Config struct {\n\tPort                  string\n\tEnableTLS             bool\n\tTLSCert               string\n\tTLSKey                string\n\tMaxConcurrentRequests int\n\tDebug                 bool\n}\n\nfunc DefaultConfig() *Config {\n\treturn &Config{\n\t\tPort:                  \":8080\",\n\t\tEnableTLS:             false,\n\t\tMaxConcurrentRequests: 1000,\n\t\tDebug:                 false,\n\t}\n}","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/config.go","time":{"start":1775852171869,"end":1775852171889}}}}
